o-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cjb1665702610334.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cjb1665702610334.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cjb1665702610334.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cjb1665702610334\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n    Break Frame </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Break Frame is a development object in a Form or Report component that is used to\n    display conditional information when a page break is encountered. A component can have multiple\n    break frames. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__section_x5d_vns_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1034793e51\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__image_hdj_d4s_mwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/print_break.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">pbr</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"euw1665702582150.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/euw1665702582150.html\" title=\"A Form is a stateful presentation Component that enables users to view and modify data in a Windows or character mode application.\">Form</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rvk1665702582227.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rvk1665702582227.html\" title=\"A Report is a Component that defines the content and layout of printed output of a Uniface application. It is not interactive and cannot be used to update the database.\">Report</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wza1665703030894.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wza1665703030894.html\" title=\"A Non-Database Entity is an Entity that has its Database Behavior property set to F. It can be used to model a group of controls, constant data, derived data, or non-persistent data that do not need to be stored in a database. It cannot be mapped to a database table.\">Non-Database Entity</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gya1665702610097.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gya1665702610097.html\" title=\"A Frame is a Development Object that graphically represents a Development Object in the layout of a Form or Report component.\">Frame</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjb1665702610334__table_d10640e1_d10641e1_d10642e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">cpt:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>/pbr:<var class=\"keyword varname\">PrintBreakId</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__section_vvh_24s_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1034793e287\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__p_d95930e1_d95931e1_d95932e1\">Print Break specializes Frame in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__ul_qwp_f4s_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__li_d38768e1_d38769e1_d38770e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__p_d95933e1_d95934e1_d95935e1\">Its can only have a Form or Report component as\n            parent object.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__li_d38771e1_d38772e1_d38773e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__p_d95936e1_d95937e1_d95938e1\">It must have a name and belong to the UYSY namespace.\n            By default, they are called <code class=\"ph codeph\">BREAK.USYS</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">BREAK_1.USYS</code>,\n            and so on.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__li_d38774e1_d38775e1_d38776e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__p_d95939e1_d95940e1_d95941e1\">It cannot contain database entities.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__li_d38777e1_d38778e1_d38779e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__p_d95942e1_d95943e1_d95944e1\">It can have a code container with a  getFocus trigger.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__section_b2v_f4s_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1034793e331\">Properties</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__p_d95948e1_d95949e1_d95950e1\">Presentation properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__ul_gn1_h4s_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__li_d38780e1_d38781e1_d38782e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mpr1665702587008.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mpr1665702587008.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a horizontal axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Left (xpos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__li_d38783e1_d38784e1_d38785e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aon1665702587081.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aon1665702587081.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a vertical axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Top (ypos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__li_d38786e1_d38787e1_d38788e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"swp1665702587155.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swp1665702587155.html\" title=\"Width of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Width (xsize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__li_d38789e1_d38790e1_d38791e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nai1665703058765.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nai1665703058765.html\" title=\"Height of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Height (ysize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__li_d38792e1_d38793e1_d38794e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gmd1665702587249.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gmd1665702587249.html\" title=\"This property determines whether a border is displayed around the area frame, entity or occurrence frame, or field. It is set from the context menu in the form canvas.\">Border</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__li_d38795e1_d38796e1_d38797e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wwg1665702587409.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wwg1665702587409.html\" title=\"Code that identifies a Uniface index color, which represents a combination of background and foreground colors. Applicable only to Form components. Deprecated.\">Index Color</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__p_d95951e1_d95952e1_d95953e1\">Printing properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__ul_un1_h4s_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__li_d38798e1_d38799e1_d38800e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fwo1665702688306.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fwo1665702688306.html\" title=\"Determines how Uniface handles page breaks if there is not enough room to print a complete frame or occurrence.\">Page feed after occurrence</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__li_d38801e1_d38802e1_d38803e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rdh1665702703470.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rdh1665702703470.html\" title=\"Indicates whether printing is suppressed if there is no data available for this object. Valid values are True (default) or False.\">Do not print empty occurrence</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__section_drx_h4s_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1034793e435\">Triggers</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__ul_s54_34s_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cjb1665702610334__li_d38804e1_d38805e1_d38806e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"biv1665702630863.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/biv1665702630863.html\" title=\"Trigger that responds to the frame getting focus (usually when the frame is about to be printed).\">trigger getFocus (Frame)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ljw1665702610670.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Area Frames for Printing</a><p>In reports, area frames can be used to add and protect text as part of an entity in Report components.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612368\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612368\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Break Frame Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Break Frame A Break Frame is a development object in a Form or Report component that is used to display conditional information when a page break is encountered. A component can have multiple break frames. Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: pbr Main Development Object? No Part of: Form , Report Contains: Property , Code Container , Non-Database Entity Generalization: Frame Specializations: — Compilation Output: — URI format: cpt: ComponentName /pbr: PrintBreakId Specialization Print Break specializes Frame in the following ways: Its can only have a Form or Report component as parent object. It must have a name and belong to the UYSY namespace. By default, they are called BREAK.USYS , BREAK_1.USYS , and so on. It cannot contain database entities. It can have a code container with a getFocus trigger. Properties Presentation properties: Left (xpos) Top (ypos) Width (xsize) Height (ysize) Border Index Color Printing properties: Page feed after occurrence Do not print empty occurrence Triggers trigger getFocus (Frame) Related Links Area Frames for Printing In reports, area frames can be used to add and protect text as part of an entity in Report components. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}